    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1921-09-06T12:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1921-09-06T12:00:00-05:00" n="29"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d29">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.62119/64: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Herrick</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-09-06T18:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 6, 1921—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 6:48 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>539. Department’s telegram no. 404, August 26.<note n="19" xml:id="d29fn19">See
                        footnote 16, <ref target="#pg_24">p. 24</ref>.</note> Briand’s absence has
                    delayed a reply. I gather that the French think that the Allied Powers must be
                    consulted and that identic action should be taken, and that they have already so
                    informed the Belgians. Article in newspaper here this afternoon was inspired by
                    leak from Belgian sources, but I understand that the Foreign Office is
                    publishing correction.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Herrick</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
